</ul></nav></section><section class="front-matter"><div class="ameta p font-secondary font-xs">
<hgroup><h1>Trends in Comorbidity, Disability, and Polypharmacy in Heart Failure</h1></hgroup><div class="cg p">
<a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Wong%20CY"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id1"><span class="name western">Catherine Y Wong</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id1">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Catherine Y Wong</span>, <span class="degrees">BS</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>a</sup> Weill Cornell Medical College, New York, NY</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Wong%20CY"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Catherine Y Wong</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>a</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Chaudhry%20SI"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id2"><span class="name western">Sarwat I Chaudhry</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id2">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Sarwat I Chaudhry</span>, <span class="degrees">MD</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>b</sup> Section of General Medicine, Department of Internal Medicine, Yale University School of Medicine, New Haven, Conn</div>
<div class="p">Find articles by <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Chaudhry%20SI"[Author]' class="usa-link"><span class="name western">Sarwat I Chaudhry</span></a>
</div>
</div>
<sup>b</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Desai%20MM"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id3"><span class="name western">Mayur M Desai</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id3">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Mayur M Desai</span>, <span class="degrees">PhD, MPH</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>c</sup> Division of Chronic Disease Epidemiology, School of Public Health, Yale University School of Medicine, New Haven, Conn</div>
