</div>
</div>
<sup>c</sup>, <a href='https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/?term="Krumholz%20HM"[Author]' class="usa-link" aria-describedby="id4"><span class="name western">Harlan M Krumholz</span></a><div hidden="hidden" id="id4">
<h3>
<span class="name western">Harlan M Krumholz</span>, <span class="degrees">MD, SM</span>
</h3>
<div class="p">
<sup>d</sup> Section of Cardiovascular Medicine, Department of Internal Medicine, Yale University School of Medicine, New Haven, Conn</div>
